      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Nationality, culture, and styles that originated in Campania, located in southern Italy, on the Tyrrhenian Sea between the Garigliano River and the Gulf of Policastro.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
